&lt;p>Reference&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>LlamaIndex接入千帆RAG</title><link>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/ai/llamaindex%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%A5%E5%8D%83%E5%B8%86rag/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 01:52:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/ai/llamaindex%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%A5%E5%8D%83%E5%B8%86rag/</guid><description>&lt;p>记录从使用Llama-index框架, 基于在线文心千帆大模型ERNIE-4.0, 构建实现本地知识检索.&lt;/p>
